{"type": "article", "id": 5616, "title": "Run-D.M.C. 乐高玩偶", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-28T07:56:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234053dQac8voh6EZ3G0yK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t为了向美国传奇说唱组合 Run-D.M.C. 致敬，设计师 Matthias Haun 最近特别设计了一套 Run-D.M.C. 的乐高玩偶，包括一个微型舞台与 Run-D.M.C. 三位传奇歌手 Joseph Simmons、Darryl McDaniels 和 Jam Master Jay 的模型。设计师为三位歌手设计了他们常穿的 adidas 服饰以及金项链等配饰，整套模型由 400 块乐高积木构成。目前，乐高公司为 Run-D.M.C. 玩偶开启了项目征集页面，只要该项目手机到 1 万名用户的投票支持，乐高就会将其量产化。感兴趣的朋友可以<a href=\"https://ideas.lego.com/projects/92213\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里参与支持</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234051cC4DzeBiUHnG2yMw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340527O3l2AFuXIZ0CEdv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340523bqfZHGpmitPMz4h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234052iBGyYF6UZhckPxMv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}